tournamentInfo.sponsorDesc:
We invite you to participate in this tournament to help us raise vital funds to create space and programs in hospitals nationwide that focus on teens and young adults affected by cancer. By participating 100% of your funds go directly back to Teen Cancer America! 

All prizes below can be picked up at Redmond Ridge once the tournament has completed. Note: tiebreakers will go to a scorecard comparison based upon handicap holes.

Questions or support please contact us at: support@actiongolfers.com
tournamentInfo.webPageBlob: Teen Cancer America engages and supports hospitals and outpatient facilities in the development of specialized and comprehensive care programs for ages 13-39. Teen Cancer builds friendly environments
